{"aid": "igkovwv8oeztm", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 3, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6tx0nskPKr", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "content": "<p>我最开始对于多核处理的进程和线程的理解是&#xff1a; 系统<strong>只可以</strong>执行一个进程&#xff0c;通过快速的上下文切换实现多进程。但是线程可以同时在多核处理上并发执行&#xff0c;也就是说不需要进行上下文切换即可实现多线程同步的进行。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>后来又翻书查看了一下&#xff0c;一下是查看的段落&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i6tx0nskPKr/i6txgwwptftf/1.png\" /></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>以下是1.9.1的段落&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i6tx0nskPKr/i6txm3e6wl9q/2.png\" /></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>看完以后对于多核处理器的进程执行产生了迷惑。在多核处理下&#xff0c;是否还是只执行一个进程&#xff1f;超线程处理器是否是用并行的技术实现单核超线程&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": "有关于多核处理器下&#xff0c;进程与线程的概念。"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634594340, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "id": "i6ua99beksj7bo", "tag_endorse": [{"name": "钟声华", "id": "i6tx0nskPKr", "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": false, "us": false}, {"name": "crazyx", "id": "i6vm0bo5WgQ", "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": false, "us": false}, {"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "name": "Yu Chen", "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "photo": "1378950179_35.png", "admin": true, "us": false}, {"name": "hbisheng", "id": "i70lz5f0QKm", "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": false, "us": false}], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hsfa0sawctb6v4", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "content": "<p>可以分为 <strong>操作系统</strong> 和 <strong>硬件</strong> 两个层面来考虑这个问题。</p>\n<p>从 <strong>操作系统</strong> 层面&#xff0c;大部分操作系统工作时都有多个进程&#xff0c;进程的执行需要靠处理器</p>\n<p>一般情况&#xff0c;单核处理器&#xff0c;一个瞬间执行着一个进程&#xff0c;而在更长的时间内可能交替执行了多个进程</p>\n<p>考虑多核处理&#xff0c;每个核的情况同单核处理器&#xff0c;但是由于有多个核&#xff0c;所以整机实际上一个瞬间执行着多个进程</p>\n<p>简单来说&#xff0c;一个处理器在执行一个进程的时候&#xff0c;硬件资源是未能很充分地利用起来的&#xff0c;所以超线程从 <strong>硬件</strong> 层面来理解是让处理器具备了同时执行多个线程的能力</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": ["i6tx0nskPKr", "i6vm0bo5WgQ", "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "i70lz5f0QKm"], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "id": "i6yho2eh2a72lv", "updated": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "subject": "这里需要对“并行 parallel”和“并发 concurrent”两个概念很清楚。", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 8, "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 171, "created": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "id": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 19, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["quiz1"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6tx0nskPKr", "when": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "data": "i6txptmz8zn3m4", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hsfa0sawctb6v4", "when": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "data": "i6ua99bhl747bp", "to": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "when": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "to": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["quiz1", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 1, "tag_good": []}}